OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,FViolence and abuse against retail
OL,7,Fworkers fell by a fifth last year but
OL,8,Fremains "unacceptably high".
OL,10,FAccording to the British Retail
OL,11,FConsortium (BRC) Crime Report,
OL,12,Fpublished on Tuesday, incidents
OL,13,Finvolving physical violence against
OL,14,Fretail staff remained largely
OL,15,Funchanged from the previous year, at
OL,16,F118 per day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
