FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771967126
OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,FThe BRC hailed "hard-won" progress
OL,7,Fthat resulted in the overall number of
OL,8,Fincidents falling from 2,000 a day to
OL,9,F1,600, but said levels remained
OL,10,F"unacceptably high" - and far beyond
OL,11,Fthe 455 incidents a day registered
OL,12,Fbefore the pandemic.
OL,14,FThe improvement reflected 13% of
OL,15,Fretailers rating the police response
OL,16,Fto incidents as good or excellent, up
OL,17,Ffrom 9% in last year's report.
OL,26,@nD@POUnD@YO]rD@AOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
