OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771967126
OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,FRetailers had also spent more than #5
OL,7,Fbillion in the last five years on
OL,8,Fimproved security measures, including
OL,9,FCCTV and security staff, and the
OL,10,Finvestment was "starting to pay off".
OL,12,FTheft remained a significant
OL,13,Fchallenge, with 5.5 million detected
OL,14,Fincidents last year, costing retailers
OL,15,Fnearly #400 million.
OL,17,FThe BRC said many incidents went
OL,18,Fundetected, and the true cost was
OL,19,Flikely much higher.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
