OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771967126
OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Violence remains endemic. No
OL,8,Fone should go to work fearing for
OL,9,Ftheir safety, and we must redouble our
OL,10,Fefforts to bring these numbers much
OL,11,Ffurther down once and for all.
OL,13,F"Theft remains a huge issue, with an
OL,14,Fincreasingly concerning link to
OL,15,Forganised criminal gangs, who continue
OL,16,Fto systematically target one store
OL,17,Fafter another, stealing tens of
OL,18,Fthousands of pounds worth of goods in
OL,19,Fone go.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
