SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771967126
OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,F"Retailers, the police and government
OL,7,Fmust continue to work together,
OL,8,Fbuilding on the great work done so
OL,9,Ffar, focusing on consistent
OL,10,Fenforcement, better data and
OL,11,Fintelligence sharing, and targeted
OL,12,Faction against prolific offenders and
OL,13,Forganised gangs."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
