FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771967126
OL,3,CAbuse against retailers falls by a
OL,4,Cfifth, but still 'unacceptably high'
OL,6,F"Having to deal with repeated and
OL,7,Fpersistent offences can cause issues
OL,8,Fbeyond the theft itself, like anxiety,
OL,9,Ffear and physical harm to retail
OL,10,Fworkers."
OL,12,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,13,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,14,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,15,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
